    "sidepanelcontent": "[hr]\r\n[b]Creature Type:[/b] Humanoid (Therianborn)[br]\r\n[b]Size: [/b]Small (about 2-3 feet tall)[br]\r\n[b]Speed:[/b] 25 feet[br]\r\n\r\nAs a Puffari you have these special traits.[br]\r\n\r\n[b]Tumbleweed Dodge.[/b] When an enemy targets you with an attack, you can use your reaction to roll into a ball of fur and sand, imposing disadvantage on the attack roll. If the attack still misses, you can immediately move 10 feet without provoking opportunity attacks.[br]\r\n[b]Sandstep Agility. [/b]You ignore movement penalties from difficult terrain, additionally, when you use the Dash action, you can move through enemy spaces without provoking opportunity attacks.[br]\r\n[b]Sun-Blessed Fur.  [/b]You have resistance to radiant damage. Additionally, you do not suffer exhaustion from extreme heat.[br]\r\n[b]Trickster’s Tongue. [/b] Choose one of the following features to define your Puffari’s natural talents:\r\n[ul][li][b]Silver-Tongued Liar.[/b] You have advantage on Deception checks[/li][/ul]\r\n[ul][li][b]Magical Trickster.[/b] You know the Vicious Mockery cantrip[/li][/ul]",
